						               													<description>It's December 15th, Christmas is almost upon us, but the house is not ready to celebrate yet!&amp;#10;The tree is in its place ... but it's bare!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In these 10 days you will have to decorate your tree in the best possible way, filling it with lights and balls to make it the most beautiful in the city!&amp;#10;But it won't be easy ... as it has to shine the same colors both night and day, the balls you place on the tree will have the same color of the light in that spot.&amp;#10;Remember not to close the curtains! If Santa sees a ball he likes, he will reward you with gifts and decorations!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game consists of placing the various Christmas lights tiles on the tree.&amp;#10;Depending on the predominant color on each single intersection of the various triangles, players will be able to place balls of a color, ornaments for the room or receive gifts from Santa Claus. All this will allow players to earn points to win the match.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Who will be able to make the most beautiful tree? &amp;#10;We will find out only after unwrapping the gifts!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
